==Usage==
This is a subtemplate of {{tl|Infobox settlement}}.  It is not intended to be used directly.  It is called by the following subtemplates.
*{{tl|Infobox settlement/areadisp}}
*{{tl|Infobox settlement/densdisp}}
*{{tl|Infobox settlement/lengthdisp}}
It displays a quantity in terms of imperial/US customary units and metric units.  The imperial/US customary units are first with the metric units in brackets as determined by {{tl|Infobox settlement/pref}}. 

It takes the following parameters.
*<code><nowiki>{{{metv}}}</nowiki></code> (required) — the numerical value of the metric value
*<code><nowiki>{{{impv}}}</nowiki></code> (required) — the numerical value of the imperial/US value
*<code><nowiki>{{{metu}}}</nowiki></code> (optional: defaults to "m") — the symbol/abbreviation of the metric unit (or inverse unit)
*<code><nowiki>{{{impu}}}</nowiki></code> (optional: defaults to "ft") — the symbol/abbreviation of the imperial/US unit (or inverse unit)
*<code><nowiki>{{{s}}}</nowiki></code> (optional: defaults to a non-breaking space) — the separator between numeral and (inverse) unit: set to "/" for inverse units

